<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- qadĩmūạ lilrãbĩ sub̊ḥaⁿạ
 wasujūdaⁿạ qad̊ wajab̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ bidamihi fadānā
 ḥāmilạaⁿ ʿanãạ ạl̊gẖaḍab̊

[V2]
 2- qadĩmūạ ḥam̊daⁿạ wasẖuk̊raⁿạ
 lilãdẖī qadi ạr̊taqay̱
 min̊ ạảʿ̊māqi ạl̊qab̊ri qāma
 ṣāʿidaⁿạ ại̹lay̱ ạlsãmā

[V3]
 3- māta ʿanãạ ḥīna kunãạ
 ạl̊kulũ ạảm̊wātaⁿạ kẖuṭāh̊
 wabimaẘtihi ḥabā man̊
 kāna maẙtaⁿạ ạl̊ḥayāh̊

[V4]
 4- māniḥaⁿạ lanā maqāmaⁿạ
 maʿ̊hu dākẖila ạl̊ḥijāb̊
 walanā yā̊̉tī sarīʿaⁿạ
 lil̊kẖalạṣi ạl̊mus̊taṭāb̊

[V5]
 5- majĩdūhu karĩmūhu
 wal̊nuqadĩr̊ fiʿ̊lahu
 ạudẖ̊kurūhu farĩḥūhu
 wal̊nuʿaẓĩm̊ sẖakẖ̊ṣahu</lyrics>
<title>qdmwạ llrb sbḥạ</title>
